Package: njord
Title: Parametric Windstorm Trigger Design and Basis Risk Quantification
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Campbell", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "m.campbell@tutanota.com")
Description: Hazard modelling, parametric trigger design, and basis risk
    quantification for UK/European windstorm using ERA5/Copernicus CDS data.
    Fits negative binomial frequency and GPD severity models to historical
    storm footprints, defines tiered gust-speed payout schedules, benchmarks
    against an MDR-based indemnity loss model, and decomposes basis risk by
    source (geographic resolution, aggregation window, trigger functional form).
